title: Andy Warhol Portrait Neon Scarf
description:
Think you're seeing double? That's just as he intended. Pop art icon Andy Warhol (American, 1928 - 1987) was known for an ad-inspired, whimsical style often involving multiple, repeating motifs. Add edge to any outfit with a scarf inspired by his signature style. Poly blend.

31 x 69 in.
